Comments.Message: Didn't I already do this one?

Item #20239 only covered item drops from the dungeon instances (not any of the raids).  Many of these had been fixed by commit 58632 on March 10 but were later undone.  Others (like the legs from Maloriak) were reported in item 20202 and were said to be fixed in your local build but did not appear to make it into the most recent round of checked in changes.
